title: Launch a DEX Course
body:
I propose Launching a 1 Month DEX Course.

The course will teach participants how to create and launch their own functioning Decentralized Exchange. The DEX will be modeled after Uniswap V2.

Course Teacher: Antoine
Course TA's: Violeta, Skiing888, Kedar

At the end, students who pass will receive a "Certified DEX Developer" Certificate. (non destructible and non transferable)
author: 0x2c8a7fE54782D63a4a5B0F1677C0D65A33421F60
